210
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:27,840
You've gotten dark too.

211
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:29,200
It must have been tough.

212
00:12:30,800 --> 00:12:31,640
Silly girl,

213
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:32,800
