214
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:36,120
I've earned money
to buy you delicious food

215
00:12:36,120 --> 00:12:37,160
and pretty clothes.

216
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:38,080
Look!

217
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:39,800
I got them for you!

218
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:47,880
Baoyin!

219
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:50,160
Luo.

220
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:51,640
You finally returned.

221
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:52,960
I didn't just return.

222
00:12:53,040 --> 00:12:54,320
I've got a ton of gifts for you.

223
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,720
All this seafood is yours.

224
00:12:56,800 --> 00:12:57,760
What do you want to eat?

225
00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:59,040
- I'll cook.
- Baoyin,

226
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:01,240
Su said

227
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:02,360
if you're back,

228
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:04,800
