234
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:18,040
I'll cook tonight to welcome you.

235
00:13:18,040 --> 00:13:19,080
Come back early.

236
00:13:57,200 --> 00:13:58,200
I bought this.

237
00:14:23,560 --> 00:14:24,320
