with the ship.

240
00:14:45,480 --> 00:14:47,880
The Shu brocade you ordered
from the Curio Shop last month

241
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:49,600
should be ready by now.

242
00:14:51,520 --> 00:14:53,160
I'll go get it for you.

243
00:14:56,400 --> 00:14:58,120
Good that you remembered for me.

244
00:14:59,360 --> 00:14:59,960
Go.

245
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:01,440
Yes.

246
00:16:06,160 --> 00:16:07,200
Mr. Wen Junior.

